Nkitobirat pee esheti enkaji e Nkai

(
1   Ilai 
5  .
1  -
18  )


1  Neitobir apa Solomon pee eshet enkaji e Nkai tenkaraki enkarna o Laitoriani, neitobiraki kewan enkaji e nkitoo. 
2  Neiteng'el Solomon iltung'ana nkalifuni ntomoni naapishana pee enap ilolan, neiteng'el iltung'ana nkalifuni ntomoni isiet pee eturu isoito teina kop oo ndonyio, neiteng'el iltung'ana nkalifuni uni o iip ile ooitasheiki ninche. 
3  Neirriwaki Solomon olkilikuai Huram olaiguanani le Turo: Nejoki, “Ore apa anaa enintaasa Daudi papa, nirriwaki ninye iltarakua ooshetie enkaji enye nabikie, ntaasaki sii nanu ina.


4  “Ng'ura etaa nanu kajo pee ashet enkaji tenkaraki enkarna o Laitoriani Enkai ai, naitisinya nanu ninye apejoki enkorropil, o sonkoyoni naarropil te dukuya ninye. Naishoru nanu anaake emukate enkitoduaarato, naishoru nanu ilasarri oopejori tadekenya o teipa, too sabatoni o too lapaitin ng'ejuko, o too siruai gelunot lo Laitoriani Enkai ang, anaa apa enaiteng'elaki ntarasi te Israel. 
5  Ore ina aji nalo nanu ashet naa keaku kitok, amu ore Enkai ang naa aikitok alang nkaitin pooki. 
6   Kake aing'ae oidim ateshetaki ninye keper, aa ore keper nalakua oleng nemeishaa? Kara nanu ng'ae oshetaki ninye enkaji, aa ore meteleku ake ewueji nepejieki enkorropil te dukuya ninye? 
7  Ore naa taata irriwakaki nanu oltung'ani arriyia te siaai e sahabu, o enkosholai, o suyai, o sekenkei, o too muain pilei o naanyokie o nkilani pusi oltung'ani oiteng'enaki te nguetare, pee elo aaku tenebo lelo aisiaayiak arriyiak ootii tenebo nanu te Yuda o te Yerusalem, lelo apa ooishorua Daudi papa lai. 
8  Irriwakaki sii iltarakua o lkeek oonyaanyukie iltarakua, o mbaoi naaing'uaa Lebanon, amu ayiolo nanu ajo keyiolo isinkan linono aatudung mbaoi te Lebanon. Naa keaku isinkan laainei tenebo isinkan linono, 
9  pee aaitobiraki nanu mbaoi kumok, amu ore ina aji nalo nanu ashet naa keaku kitok naa enenking'asia. 
10  Naa kaishoru nanu tenkaraki isinkan linono, lelo oodung'u mbaoi, mpirbili nkalifuni tikitam e nkano naidong'o, o mpirbili nkalifuni tikitam e shairi, o mboreitin iip ong'uan oltulet le naisho oo sabibu, o eilata mboreitin iip ong'uan oltulet.”


11  Neitoki Huram ilo aiguanani le Turo awal te mpalai naigeroko Solomon, nejo, “Ore enkaraki nanyor Olaitoriani iltung'ana lenyena, kintaa iyie olaiguanani lenye.” 
12  Neitoki Huram, ajo, “Meisisi Olaitoriani Enkai e Israel, ilo oitobira shumata o enkop, laa ninye oishoo olaiguanani Daudi olayioni ng'en, neiputaki enkarriyiano o eyiolounoto, laa ninye oshetaki Olaitoriani enkaji, neshetaki kewan enkaji e nkitoo.


13  “Airriwua naa taata nanu oltung'ani arriyia, obore eyiolounoto Huramabi 
14  olayioni le ntito e Dan, ore apa menye naa oltung'ani le Turo. Eiteng'enaki ninye pee easishore sahabu, o enkosholai, o suyai, o esekenkei, o soito o nkeek, o muain pooki pilei o mpusi, o nkilani naanyokie o kitani napuyiapui. Neas mpukunot pooki e nguetare nedamu enkipirunoto ake ninye naishooki ninye meipiru. Keaku lelo tung'ana linono arriyiak tenebo iltung'ana arriyiak lo lkitok lai Daudi papaai lino. 
15  Ore naa taata ina ano o shairi, o eilata o enaisho oo sabibu, naa ninche eimaka olkitok lai, nchoo ninye meirriwaki isinkan linono; 
16  naa aikidung'u iyiook mbaoi naaba anaa iniyieu te Lebanon, nikiyaki iyie too rridat aaimunye enaiposha e Yopa, pee itum iyie aawa Yerusalem.”

